address2: Longbao Shuanghekou Light Industry Park Wanzhou District
longBusinessSummary: Carpenter Tan Holdings Limited, an investment holding company, designs, manufactures, and distributes wooden handicrafts and accessories. The company offers wooden or horn combs, such as colored drawing combs, grass-and-tree dyed wooden combs, and carved combs; pocket-size wooden mirrors, including colored drawing mirrors and carved mirrors; other wooden accessories and adornments comprising bead bracelets, pendants, barrettes, hair bobs, and massage tools; and box sets that combine its products in themes for gift purpose. The company sells its products primarily under the Carpenter Tan brand name. It is also involved in the operation of retailing shops in Hong Kong and China, as well as franchise and distribution network primarily in the People's Republic of China; distribution of wooden handicrafts and accessories through internet; and property investment activities. Carpenter Tan Holdings Limited was founded in 1997 and is based in Chongqing, the People's Republic of China.
